Package: exaro-plugins
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: eXaro it's a free reporting solution for Qt, released under GPLv3 license.
 eXaro can be embedded very easy in any Qt application.
 eXaro has an integrated preview with search and export (in different formats) capabilities

